abstract = {A novel method has been developed to allow the accurate determination
	of equilibrium gas-phase structures from experimental data, thus
	allowing direct comparison with theory. This new method is illustrated
	through the example of sodium chloride vapor at 943 K. Using this
	approach the equilibrium structures of the monomer (NaCl) and the
